<subSubSection box="[199,1430,1944,1969]" pageId="8" pageNumber="89" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1367,1969]" box="[199,1430,1944,1969]" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1944,1969]" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">Etymology.</emphasis>
A combination of the Latin words: 
<emphasis box="[735,789,1944,1968]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">latus</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[844,916,1944,1968]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="89">tabula</emphasis>
, reference to the surstylus broadened distally.
</paragraph>
